				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-Trang/B%E1%BB%87nh-h%E1%BA%ADu-ph%E1%BB%8Fng-mai-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-d7ZuADEaLeCD4F6EqnVtAA">Bệnh hậu phỏng mai kỳ 1 - 病後訪梅其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-Trang/author-QKy6LHJMqAcMRcgSw6RXSA">Lưu Khắc Trang</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/%C4%90%E1%BA%AFc-gia-th%C6%B0-th%E1%BB%8B-nh%E1%BA%ADt-t%C3%A1c/poem-w52NGg4k0na_rajDMu1bmg">Đắc gia thư, thị nhật tác - 得家書是日作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-C%C3%B4ng-H%C3%A3ng/H%C3%A0m-%C4%90an-ho%C3%A0i-c%E1%BB%95/poem-dQTjlz1YM5YxSF0zkZqHuA">Hàm Đan hoài cổ - 邯鄲懷古</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-C%C3%B4ng-H%C3%A3ng/author-fN6vfxH4UNedI1oRF5kt2Q">Nguyễn Công Hãng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-Hi%E1%BA%BFu-V%E1%BA%A5n/Ph%C3%B3ng-ng%C3%B4n/poem-eVvgjy2SreWudA8ciPrP7A">Phóng ngôn - 放言</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-Hi%E1%BA%BFu-V%E1%BA%A5n/author-lCIs61Hzjl6rqKSiwGq6ow">Nguyên Hiếu Vấn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Sa-Uy%E1%BB%83n-h%C3%A0nh/poem-wnnk6Eq0kRHPGKi6f4N1FQ">Sa Uyển hành - 沙苑行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/Thi%C3%AAn-v%C3%A2n-v%E1%BA%A1n-thu%E1%BB%B7-gian/poem-ugRfi601e7To8GsJFZCPtQ">Thiên vân vạn thuỷ gian - 千雲萬水間</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/author-o98HuijKnTRKdgvHyXbEYw">Hàn Sơn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-H%E1%BB%AFu-Tr%C3%A1c/Th%E1%BB%A7-27/poem-PbnBF1cQAQRZQjVQRoIsqg">Thủ 27 - 首２７</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-H%E1%BB%AFu-